<template>
  Home
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'
import { ref } from '@vue/reactivity';
export default {
  name: 'HomePage',
  emits:['loginData'],
  setup(props, {emit}) {
    let loginCheck = ref(true);
    axios.get('/api/customer/login-check').then(res=>{
      console.log(res.data);
      emit('loginData', res.data);
    }).catch(err=>{
      console.log(err);
    });
    
    return {}
  }
}
</script>
